caption:
Looking for work and not sure how to put together a resume? We can help.

Through our Community Integration program, volunteers like Julia offer one-on-one support to people writing a resume for the first time or updating one they used back home.

This service is free!

If you're interested in updating your resume or if you're an employer or recruiter who wants to connect with us about workforce support, email Belinda at belinda@welcomeimmigrant.org.
